Rules.InvariantScript:
"data:image/svg+xml; utf-8, " & EncodeUrl("<svg width='46' height='39' viewBox='0 0 46 39' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
<path d='M23 39L0.483337 0L45.5167 0L23 39Z' fill='"& DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.ErrorIcon.Color &"'/>
</svg>
")

"data:image/svg+xml;utf8, " & EncodeUrl(
    "<svg id='Close' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='24' height='24' viewBox='0 0 24 24'>
  <path id='Path_65' data-name='Path 65' d='M0,0H24V24H0Z' fill='none'/>
  <path id='Path_66' data-name='Path 66' d='M19,6.41,17.59,5,12,10.59,6.41,5,5,6.41,10.59,12,5,17.59,6.41,19,12,13.41,17.59,19,19,17.59,13.41,12Z' fill='"& If(DatePickerComponent.DisplayMode = "Error",DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.CloseIcon.ErrorColor,DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.CloseIcon.Color) &"'/>
</svg>
"
)

If(
    Value(Self.Text) > 31,
    Reset(Self),If(IsBlank(gblDateSelected),Set(
        gblDateSelected,
        DateValue(
            Text(
                Concatenate(
                    Value(Self.Text),
                    "/",
                    Text(Now(),"mm"),
                    "/",
                    Text(Now(),"yyyy")
                ),
                "dd/mm/yyyy"
            ),"en-GB"
        )
    ),
    Set(
        gblDateSelected,
        DateValue(
            Text(
                Concatenate(
                    Value(Self.Text),
                    "/",
                    txtMonthInputDP.Text,
                    "/",
                    txtYearInputDP.Text
                ),
                "dd/mm/yyyy"
            ),"en-GB"
        )
    )
))

"data:image/svg+xml,"
&
EncodeUrl("<svg width='8' height='14' viewBox='0 0 8 14' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
<path d='M7.5 14L0.5 7L7.5 0L7.5 14Z' fill='"& DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.DatePicker.BackNextIcon.Fill &"'/>
</svg>
")

"data:image/svg+xml,"
&
EncodeUrl("<svg width='8' height='14' viewBox='0 0 8 14' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'>
<path d='M0.5 0L7.5 7L0.5 14L0.5 0Z' fill='"& DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.DatePicker.BackNextIcon.Fill &"'/>
</svg>

")

ControlPropertyState.AutoRuleBindingString: If(Self.Layout = Layout.Horizontal, Min(320, Self.Width - 60), Min(320, Self.Height - 60))

Rules.InvariantScript:
{
    HeadingLabel: gblControlStyles.ControlLabel,
    DatePicker: gblControlStyles.DatePicker,
    CloseIcon: gblControlStyles.CloseIcon,
    ErrorIcon: gblControlStyles.ErrorIcon,
    ErrorMessagePopup: gblControlStyles.ErrorMessagePopup
}

If(
    DatePickerComponent.Opened,
    If(
        DatePickerComponent.ErrorOpened,
        DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.DatePicker.Height + 40,
        DatePickerComponent.StylingProperty.DatePicker.Height
    ),
    If(
        DatePickerComponent.ErrorOpened,
        102,
        62
    )
)
